<subSubSection id="E6E620580EE850F0296583B2C1B3E90D" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph id="109191F1F96E11496CA0CCE9B4BB1A8E" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
<taxonomicName id="A580A419235A54CEE6F26EB309826F39" authority="Holandre" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Orobanchaceae" genus="Orobanche" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="teucrii">
Orobanche 
<normalizedToken id="DCAD2649E127DCB6422DEBD8F6CA6F40" originalValue="Teúcrii" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Teucrii</normalizedToken>
Holandre
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D4EA3DE944CD1F70425A5FBE63F9E4F7" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="787EA9815FA6EDD846F61635808D3450" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Gamander-Sommerwurz</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="AB10502D707C03C61243062B43AA0306" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" type="description">
<paragraph id="A71F6C389FEEB2A3A45A4A541F9F5939" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
Stengel 10-30 cm hoch, gelb. Tragblatt ⅔ bis fast so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="2B5ED9F93ABA38F6271B50FF1676CA9D" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Bluete</normalizedToken>
, 
<emphasis id="FBA756660E8B0622BF43A29E25EC687F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">am Grunde 5</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="446FC2E0AB5C1DBA9629CCC2B268353A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">7 mm breit.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="A2E7D640D09F0A3296F2359131CE91F4" originalValue="Vorblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Vorblaetter</normalizedToken>
nicht vorhanden. Kelch wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="EF2AFD273AA852C2294E59F1D84FA7A5" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Orobanchaceae" genus="Orobanche" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cernua">
<emphasis id="692D8E015A0934CDAAF63EED72791CCA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">O. cernua</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 4). Krone 15-30 mm lang, oberhalb des Fruchtknotens 5-8 mm im Durchmesser, meist nur am Grunde und kurz vor dem Rand deutlich gebogen, dazwischen gerade, mit hellen 
<normalizedToken id="9457DF613BEB75208883AD1AE93F814A" originalValue="Drüsenhaaren" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Druesenhaaren</normalizedToken>
, 
<emphasis id="E0E941900F9479D39D6422FA25BDBA66" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
gelb bis braunlila; der mittlere Zipfel der Unterlippe 
<normalizedToken id="3DA3566C429081AEF200499B2BDA60C7" originalValue="größer" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">groesser</normalizedToken>
als die beiden seitlichen.
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="CF51C5122245BA52063F1CFE4C2172F3" originalValue="Staubfäden" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Staubfaeden</normalizedToken>
3-6 mm 
<normalizedToken id="5720D0D04ED92A839620E8013E70F6C8" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">ueber</normalizedToken>
dem Grund der Krone 
<normalizedToken id="43F9ED6010B8E2602D0AA9CDD04B24C1" originalValue="eingefügt" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">eingefuegt</normalizedToken>
, bis fast zur Mitte mit 
<normalizedToken id="06310484CF24A762EBF3791192F88022" originalValue="drüsenlosen" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">druesenlosen</normalizedToken>
Haaren. 
<emphasis id="0058C3597B925E699DA0FF839EBECF5E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Narbe braun bis purpurn.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="5AEFF019C2CBCA359389367211D54035" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="144A7B1E3A07D10ECD2F23606AF0237E" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
<emphasis id="E0FEB8488B8D60859AE971F84073948E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D47CF035DB72327F44736EC81EAE10A0" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
<emphasis id="54DA42DF3A982AFF3AC9149A88BA7AD2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan, seltener subalpin. Lockere, trockene, kalkreiche 
<normalizedToken id="8FD6A7870304C260041E946330D64978" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Trockenwiesen (Xerobrometen). - Auf Arten der Gattungen 
<taxonomicName id="8299B018661EF3F15FECFE057E51A1EB" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lamiaceae" genus="Teucrium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="A8D2984C4A8775291876766E606BF81A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Teucrium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(besonders 
<taxonomicName id="93191354D4838DD7963BB5D83EB85F75" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lamiaceae" genus="Teucrium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="chamaedrys">
<emphasis id="F7C83CCF9933C61791285F1F90F11AF6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">T. Chamaedrys</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
und 
<taxonomicName id="4CA90C368A18C2E42A961F8149342276" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lamiaceae" genus="Teucrium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="montanum">
<emphasis id="9B32AC271B96169352516C38C5284383" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">T. montanum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) sowie 
<taxonomicName id="0C28212506747E90984E21BF6B8E3C56" class="Insecta" family="Eulophidae" genus="Thymus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="9AE2BDBF4994042673B43EBA7519AFC2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Thymus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
und 
<emphasis id="7B8FFC2FBE59BA30976072C9A0AE191B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
<taxonomicName id="032877D8A7795DF223283FC1BC6CF77A" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lamiaceae" genus="Satureja" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Satureja</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4AF9EB541F32F58A6056FA18FDFD3FE7" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
<emphasis id="5CF049DA2F1EA2A43F3F0B7B1E26C63A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="71154534A91F4470FAE978D40CA4B4C4" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="A7D6D39A8E212FFA1F1AD349DAA85B1F" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, Plateau Central, Ardennen, Vogesen, Schwarzwald, Jura, Alpen, Apuanische Alpen, Karpaten, Gebirge der Balkanhalbinsel. - Im Gebiet: Alpen, Alpenvorland, Jura, Gegend von Genf, Gegend von Belfort, Oberrheinische Tiefebene, Nordschweiz, Baar, Bodenseegebiet (Argenauen); nicht 
<normalizedToken id="B817931EEC9E3A65AC5069E62B9F94A3" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
